{
  "stem": "4187.1",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Such and such is a Communist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Such and such is this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They absolutely flooded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So people started to disappear immediately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my-- my parents, both my mother and father were actually asked into the headquarters, the Hungarian headquarters, police headquarters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were-- they were grilled, not physically but verbally grilled for a day wanting-- They were trying to find out, you know, where money was or-- not that we-- we-- we certainly weren't-- weren't in that class.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, because doctors, they-- obviously, they're not businesspeople.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They-- they earn well, but there is no question of-- of a-- a lot of money hidden away somewhere.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, they believed them, apparently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And both came home that night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, of course, it was a horrible shock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the three of us were home together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We weren't allowed to leave the-- the house-- the-- the-- the flat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were so afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know whether we'd see them again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if we don't see them again, then what happens to us?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Anyhow, we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my parents decided that they'll try and hide us in the country.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they sent us, first, to a place quite near Pecs where we had very good friends.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we were hardly there for a few days, and, of course, someone went to the police.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there are three people who don't belong here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Check them out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or they may have just said, there's three Jews, who knows?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so the police came and took us back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my parents decided to try another place a bit further away from Pecs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Exactly the same thing happened in no time at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were back.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
